---
title: Mushroom Rigatoni Marinara Includes recyclable aluminum tray
description: This crowd-pleasing Italian-inspired baked pasta keeps prep and cleanup to a minimum, thanks to our convenient oven-ready tray. You'll toss rigatoni, mushrooms, and zucchini with tangy marinara sauce right in the tray, then bake until bubbling. Garnish with a sprinkle each of fresh parsley and Parmesan cheese, and dinner is served!
